
  Introduction:

  This is an IDE, ROM and RAM controller for A500.  IDE controller has
maximum transfer rate 750kb/sec (or up to 1mb/sec with special ROM patch -
send email to author for more detailed info).  FastRAM will speed up
machine if heavy video modes are used - 640x256 16 colors, for example.
Scheme connects to external 86pin slot of A500.

Archive includes next files:
hddmem1.iff    - logic part of hard drive and memory controller
hddmem2.iff    - RAM part of memory controller
hddmem3.iff    - kickswitcher
hddmem.english - this document

  Kickswitcher can use standard 271000 ROM chips, but you MUST have own
A600, A1200 or another machine for use its ROM image to burn ROMs to avoid
breaking copyright laws.  Kickswitcher is optional, you may simply buy
A500 kickstart ROM and replace old ROM with it.

 Scheme was tested on:

1. Р500/1mb chip ram
2. A500+/2mb chip ram
3. A500/0.5mb chip ram

 during 1.5 years and continues working now.  There were approximately 15
HDDs different sizes from different vendors tested.

